CRC/C/15/Add.247, para. 36, on the State report of the former Republic of Macedonia, 2000, 
CRC/C/15/Add.118 and on the State report of Sri Lanka, 2003, CRC/C/15/Add.207, para. 29. 
<b>15
</b></p>
