EVIDENCE%20FOR%20ACTION%202007%20drug_treatment.pdf and WHO, UNODC, 
UNAIDS, &#8220;Substitution maintenance therapy in the management of opioid dependence and 
HIV/AIDS prevention: Position paper&#8221; (2004). 
<b>44
</b></p>
